            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Maybe lua-language-server needs a bug report about noisy erroring for this situation, then. Other than relying on the rpc layer logging, there's nothing specific to do here (deduping doesn't quite make sense because each of these errors is from a different request). ",
